description: Miz Shirley Marie's Cuisine on Wheels is serving up Southern goodness to the Sacramento area. Their food is based on their southern creole roots. Miz Shirley Marie's menu features traditional southern favorites including Blackened Catfish, Hot Links, BBQ Cajun Chicken, and Shrimp Po' Boys, as well as sides like Red Beans and Rice, Mac' N Cheese and Cajun Fries. Miz Shirley Marie's mission bring something new and exciting to the greater Sacramento area. Follow them and come eat!
name: Shirley Jones
